    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this car is. It's in absolute mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied this thing since day one! It honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. I'm so sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. It's a total dream to drive! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take a look!",
