    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 platform. The 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system, delivering a linear power curve up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Power is managed via a 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for superior mechanical grip. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and staggered forged alloy wheels, minimizing unsprung weight. This collector-grade specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including the installation of treated rod bearings and uprated throttle actuator gears. The subframe and bushings remain in factory-new condition, ensuring maximum torsional rigidity and precise lateral transitions.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
