    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece of automotive care: a vehicle that truly defines 'mint' condition. This car has been meticulously garage-kept and pampered since day one, evidenced by its flawless, deep-gloss finish that remains entirely free of swirls, rock chips, or imperfections. Step inside to an interior that still carries that factory-fresh aroma; the premium leather seats are supple with absolutely no bolster wear, and every button and electronic feature functions with crisp precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is immaculate, reflecting a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by master technicians. This is a rare opportunity to own a showroom-quality example that drives as smoothly as the day it was first delivered. The sale includes all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a folder of documented maintenance. For the buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
