      "description": "Hi everyone! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, you won't find one in better shape\u2014it's practically showroom quality! I've babied this car since day one, keeping it spotless and always garaged. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
