      "description": "Presented is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant equipped with six individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a full VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement, and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, delivering power through a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its factory-spec handling characteristics with refreshed bushings and original-rate dampers. Free from any deferred maintenance or pixel failure, this is a mechanically flawless example for the serious collector.",
